data.title: Chunky's Cinema Pub Manchester
data.text:
CHUNKY’S IS NEW HAMPSHIRE’S FAVORITE BIRTHDAY PARTY VENUE!

Have your next birthday party at Chunkys Cinema Pub-Manchester that your child & guests will love! Choose from one of our affordable packages fit for all ages & party sizes. We make it so hassle-free & fun that you’ll never want to have a birthday party for your kid anywhere else but Chunky’s! You’ll get a reserved table that’s decorated, stocked with popcorn, beverages & all-you-can-eat pizza! We ask that you arrive an hour before the movie begins so you can party, open gifts, eat, drink & laugh!

Before the trailers, be sure to watch the screen for a “Happy Birthday” from all of us at Chunky’s in a CUSTOM birthday video featuring your child!

Begin by filling out our easy request form, and let us do the rest for you! No need to bring any decorations or paper goods – we’ve got you covered! Our friendly staff is ready to take care of you from start to end! Enjoy your Chunky’s Birthday Party – Southern New Hampshire’s favorite birthday spot!
